OL,7,F"I knew the moment I was put into that
OL,8,Fambulance something was seriously
OL,9,Fwrong, and I had known for a couple of
OL,10,Fweeks before that," the 42-year-old
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"The reason that the boys died was
OL,14,Fbecause of a condition called twin-to-
OL,15,Ftwin transfer, which was always a risk
OL,16,Fin identical twin pregnancies, the
OL,17,Fidea is that it's monitored.
