OL,3,CMum describes 'nightmare' of losing
OL,4,Ctwins as Wales maternity care 'lags
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"If it's spotted in time, women will
OL,8,Fgo on to have two healthy babies.
OL,9,FThat's what didn't happen in my case.
OL,10,FIt was apparent quite early on at 12
OL,11,Fweeks, but I was never referred for
OL,12,Fthe specialist care I should've been.
OL,14,F"Ultimately, the correct procedures
OL,15,Fand policies weren't in place to care
OL,16,Ffor what was a high-risk pregnancy."
OL,18,FAt the time of Ruth's pregnancy, Cwm
OL,19,FTaf Morgannwg University Health Board
OL,20,Fwas hit with scandal after .
