OL,7,FIt was placed into special measures,
OL,8,Fbut has since come out and made there.
OL,10,FHowever, a report on Tuesday, 14 May,
OL,11,Ffound Wales-wide progress on reducing
OL,12,Fthe number of babies who are stillborn
OL,13,Fhas "stalled".
OL,15,FThe joint report by Sands and Tommy's
OL,16,Ffound Wales has had the highest
OL,17,Fstillbirth rate of any UK nation since
OL,18,F2014 and highlighted "little progress
OL,19,Fon reducing rates of neonatal
OL,20,Fmortality over the past decade".
