OL,8,FTommy's joint policy unit, said: "I
OL,9,Fthink systemic is the word we would
OL,10,Fuse.
OL,12,F"We often talk about specific services
OL,13,For specific scandals, but actually
OL,14,Fwhen we look at the issues they're
OL,15,Frepeated across all services to a
OL,16,Fgreater or lesser extent.
