OL,4,Ctwins as Wales maternity care 'lags
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"We already have some good guidance
OL,8,Fout there in terms of what care should
OL,9,Flook like and when it's not being
OL,10,Fdelivered and babies are dying as a
OL,11,Fresult, that's really a key area where
OL,12,Fwe need change."
OL,14,FLooking at the whole of the UK, the
OL,15,Freport claimed at least 800 babies
OL,16,Fcould have been saved last year, and
OL,17,Fsaid the current level of pregnancy
OL,18,Floss and baby deaths is "not
OL,19,Finevitable".
