OL,7,FThe charities said while England has a
OL,8,Ftarget of halving rates of stillbirth,
OL,9,Fneonatal death, preterm birth,
OL,10,Fmaternal death and brain injury by
OL,11,F2025, compared to 2010, there is no
OL,12,Fequivalent in Wales.
OL,14,FRobert Wilson, head of the Sands and
OL,15,FTommy's joint policy unit, said: "Our
OL,16,Freport makes clear that the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment must commit to targets for
OL,18,Freducing pregnancy loss and baby
OL,19,Fdeaths and eliminating inequalities.
