OL,4,Ctwins as Wales maternity care 'lags
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,FRuth described her experience as
OL,8,F"horrendous, frightening and
OL,9,Fdevastating".
OL,11,F"I think anybody who finds out that
OL,12,Fthey're pregnant, you start living
OL,13,Feverything: first birthdays, first
OL,14,FChristmases, especially as a larger
OL,15,Ffamily," she said.
OL,17,F"To suddenly have all of that snatched
OL,18,Faway from you is awful, a terrible
OL,19,Fthing. You have to process telling
OL,20,Fpeople, telling our son. It's just an
OL,21,Fawful thing to go through."
