OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,FShe also said midwives and other
OL,8,Fhealth professionals are "owed so much
OL,9,Fby the people in charge as well".
OL,11,F"We're hearing all the time of these
OL,12,Funits being understaffed, overworked.
OL,13,FIn the report it refers to staff
OL,14,Fsickness - well it's not a surprise if
OL,15,Fthey're as stretched as they are.
OL,17,F"These are the people on the frontline
OL,18,Fworking with these women, giving the
OL,19,Fcare to these women and these babies
OL,20,Fand these families. We need to
OL,21,Fconsider them as well."
