OL,8,F2018, Cwm Taf Morgannwg University
OL,9,FHealth Board said it was "truly sorry
OL,10,Fthat Ruth feels let down by the care
OL,11,Fshe received at the former Cwm Taf
OL,12,FHealth Board".
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "Since 2019, and
OL,15,Fthe establishment of Cwm Taf Morgannwg
OL,16,FUniversity Health Board, we have
OL,17,Fworked in partnership with the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment, our staff and communities
OL,19,Fto make significant changes and
OL,20,Fimprovements in maternity and neonatal
OL,21,Fservices.
