OL,7,F"We are committed to improving
OL,8,Fmaternity and neonatal services across
OL,9,FWales," a spokesperson said. "Since
OL,10,F2023, considerable improvements have
OL,11,Fbeen made in the care and outcomes of
OL,12,Fpremature babies through the PERIPrem
OL,13,FCymru programme."
OL,15,FThe NHS describes PERIPrem (Perinatal
OL,16,FExcellence to Reduce Injury in
OL,17,FPremature Birth) Cymru as a perinatal
OL,18,Fcare pathway of 11 evidence-based
OL,19,Finterventions to reduce preterm
OL,20,Fmortality and brain injury.
